/381438_large.png?m=1717902558", "created": 1548919554, "last_modified": 1717902558}, "last_reply_by": "kenvix", "last_touched": 1719810399, "title": "TypeScript 是个人项目中最好用的编程语言", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053837", "created": 1719799330, "deleted": 0, "content": "因为可以做到既要灵活又要严谨，灵活的时候用 any ，严谨的时候用 type\r\n\r\n个人项目中既有快速迭代的需求也有长期维护的需求\r\n\r\n既可以做前端又可以做后端，前后端切换无需心智成本", "content_rendered": "<p>因为可以做到既要灵活又要严谨，灵活的时候用 any ，严谨的时候用 type</p>\n<p>个人项目中既有快速迭代的需求也有长期维护的需求</p>\n<p>既可以做前端又可以做后端，前后端切换无需心智成本</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719799687, "replies": 44, "id": 1053837}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6014, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1460, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 617760, "username": "ywx620", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ywx620", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_mini.png?m=1715690160", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_normal.png?m=1715690160", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_large.png?m=1715690160", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_xlarge.png?m=1715690160", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_xlarge.png?m=1715690160", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a99f/22ae/617760_xlarge.png?m=1715690160", "created": 1678244420, "last_modified": 1715690160}, "last_reply_by": "BeforeTooLate", "last_touched": 1719810419, "title": "鸡娃还是放养", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053880", "created": 1719803408, "deleted": 0, "content": "鸡娃(高压式教育):\r\n\r\n优点:可能在短期内提高孩子的学习成绩\r\n\r\n缺点:可能影响孩子的心理健康,抑制创造力,增加亲子关系压力\r\n\r\n放养(自由式教育):\r\n\r\n优点:有利于培养孩子的独立性和兴趣爱好\r\n\r\n缺点:可能导致学习成绩落后,缺乏规划\r\n\r\n我目前有两个孩子都是放养状态，现在孩子是过得是挺开心的，有个美好的童年。\r\n可是成绩真的是很差很差。\r\n\r\n是时候给孩子一些压力，逼一逼他们用点心学习。\r\n生怕再这样放养下去连高中都上不了。\r\n\r\n有孩子的老哥们平时都是怎么养娃的？", "content_rendered": "<p>鸡娃(高压式教育):</p>\n<p>优点:可能在短期内提高孩子的学习成绩</p>\n<p>缺点:可能影响孩子的心理健康,抑制创造力,增加亲子关系压力</p>\n<p>放养(自由式教育):</p>\n<p>优点:有利于培养孩子的独立性和兴趣爱好</p>\n<p>缺点:可能导致学习成绩落后,缺乏规划</p>\n<p>我目前有两个孩子都是放养状态，现在孩子是过得是挺开心的，有个美好的童年。\n可是成绩真的是很差很差。</p>\n<p>是时候给孩子一些压力，逼一逼他们用点心学习。\n生怕再这样放养下去连高中都上不了。</p>\n<p>有孩子的老哥们平时都是怎么养娃的？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719805730, "replies": 42, "id": 1053880}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 21943, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 5220, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 637925, "username": "undertheros3", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/undertheros3", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3da6ab76d7f7da80952c2130728a2f19?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3da6ab76d7f7da80952c2130728a2f19?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3da6ab76d7f7da80952c2130728a2f19?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1689037835, "last_modified": 1689037835}, "last_reply_by": "sxyclint", "last_touched": 17198064